'''Islam''' d [[ajjed]] ideg ttamnen medden belli [[Yakuc]] (Rebbi) d yiwen, ur yesɛi mmi-s ur yesɛi tameṭṭut. Ɣur-s lemluk i t-ttɛawanen, yuzen rrusel ɣur medden akken ad ttamnen yis-es. Rrasul aneggaru deg lislam d [[Muḥemmed]].

Isem n medden i yettamnen s lislam, inselmen. Inselmen ɣur-sen 5 n tamara (lefruḍ):

* [[Cchada]].
* [[Taẓallit]].
* [[Zzakat]].
* [[Remḍan]].
* [[Lḥeǧǧ]].

Deg lislam, yella yiwen wedlis : [[Leqran]], yella daɣen [[Lḥadit]] neɣ timucuha ɣef tudert n [[Muḥemmed]]. Inselmen ttamnen belli [[Abenǧil|Injil]] d [[Turat]] ttubeddlen, mačči am yuzen-iten Rebbi.

